  "texts": [
    "To the south east, the Pale Horse's sister ship, the Red Lion, was already out of sight.",
    "The sun was going down, a pink glow still covering the horizon, but its fading light made the water look almost pitch black.",
    "A light surf broke against the stones of the harbor's seawall.",
    "High on the shore, where the promontory formed a horseshoe shape, there was a small port, and beyond that the main wall of the city, the tower of the Castello Giustinian, and the cathedral could be seen against the blackening sky.",
    "Here, offshore, there were only the dark blue waters of the Adriatic."
